lines.text: Everybody wanna to go to Heaven, but nobody wanna die.

[to the audience]
They have such big plans for this world, and they don't include us! So what does that make you? Just another girl lining up to die.
You are so jealous of me. I'm everything you ever wanted to be.

[to the audience]
I'm perfect! But nobody in this shithole gets me, because I don't put out!
You're an advert. You're a commercial. I feel very, very sorry for you people. Good luck to you!

[to Corrine]
What you were was a concept and you've blown the concept.
Every girl should be given an electric guitar on her 16th birthday.

[lying about Jerry Jervey]
He was an old man in a young girl's world.
